<section class="protocol">
  <div class="wrap-wide">
    <div class="protocol-head">
      <span class="eyebrow voltage">The protocol</span>
      <h2>Pre. Intra. Post.<br>One <em>sachet.</em></h2>
      <p>Most stacks need three different products. IONIQ was built to do all three.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="protocol-grid">
      <div class="protocol-step">
        <div class="when"><div class="no">01</div><div class="lbl">Pre &middot; 30-60min before</div></div>
        <h3>Prime the system</h3>
        <p>Pre-load 750mg of sodium and the nootropic stack so focus is sharp before the first rep.</p>
        <div class="timing"><span><strong>1 sachet</strong> in 500ml cold water</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="protocol-step">
        <div class="when"><div class="no">02</div><div class="lbl">Intra &middot; during session</div></div>
        <h3>Hold the line</h3>
        <p>Sip throughout to replace what you sweat out. The sodium-potassium ratio matches human sweat.</p>
        <div class="timing"><span><strong>1 sachet</strong> across 60-90 min</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="protocol-step">
        <div class="when"><div class="no">03</div><div class="lbl">Post &middot; 0-30min after</div></div>
        <h3>Restore + recover</h3>
        <p>Magnesium for muscle, taurine and ALCAR for mitochondrial repair, hydroxyl ions for antioxidant load.</p>
        <div class="timing"><span><strong>1 sachet</strong> within 30 min</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% schema %}{ "name": "Pre/Intra/Post", "presets": [{ "name": "Pre/Intra/Post" }] }{% endschema %}